      -- Since $k(T)$ is the number of minority symbols in the orbit class up to time $T$, and $U$ is eventually periodic, $k(T)$ is bounded.
      have h_kT_bounded : ∃ C : ℕ, ∀ T ≥ T1, kT T ≤ C := by
